                            <comment id="15934783" author="sergey_beryozkin" created="Tue, 21 Mar 2017 15:47:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Dennis&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m just about to commit some other change to this class, please wait for may be 30 mins&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Sergey&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15934786" author="deki" created="Tue, 21 Mar 2017 15:50:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ok I&apos;ll update and rebase before creating the PR.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15934823" author="sergey_beryozkin" created="Tue, 21 Mar 2017 16:19:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Please check&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-7290&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-7290&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;By the way, if we skip Proxies, can we miss for example CGLIB-proxified JAX-RS service beans ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15934863" author="githubbot" created="Tue, 21 Mar 2017 16:44:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user deki opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cxf/pull/249&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cxf/pull/249&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

